'''''The Empire Strikes Back Monthly'' 150''' is the one hundred fiftieth issue of the ''[[The Empire Strikes Back Monthly]]'' series of comic reprints, published in [[September]] [[1981]].

As the cover tease shows, this issue was intended to include part one of "[[The Pandora Effect]]", but a note on the first page says deadline woes made it impossible to include in this issue. Instead, it reprints [[Star Wars (1977) 16|''Star Wars'' (1977) 16]]. The Pandora Effect was printed entirely in [[The Empire Strikes Back Monthly 151|''The Empire Strikes Back Monthly'' 151]].

